g songs. And the books that we read on Sundays were different from those we - were different from the generality of our books. Some were more suitable}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1246371\charrsid15356049 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
