\insrsid1246371\charrsid15356049 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3767260\charrsid15356049  were not coloured. A coloured picture was rather}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1246371\charrsid15356049 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
