\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655475 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3767260\charrsid15356049 The Daily News was a Liberal paper wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2697502 HC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3767260\charrsid15356049 Yes.
