\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655475 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3767260\charrsid15356049 Always, a lot of the Congregationals were changing over to Conservatives at that time?
