\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2697502 HC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3767260\charrsid15356049 No. No, the - the only people who came to the house were - the grandparents or - or occasionally - one or other of my father's b
