 Grand in Croydon High Street. It - it's not there now but it - it's only recently it's been taken right away. It had}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12417800\charrsid15356049 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3767260\charrsid15356049 
 over the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9663077\charrsid15356049 proscenium}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3767260\charrsid15356049  arch}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12417800\charrsid15356049 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
