\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2697502 HC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3767260\charrsid15356049 We used to - my cousin - was - the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12417800\charrsid15356049 daughter}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3767260\charrsid15356049  of a - the captain of a tea clipper. Which had been a tea clipper, one of those that had - had - they were rather famous I think, that plied between Britain and China. And the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
