parents - never really - or my father never raised his }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7633170\charrsid15356049 voice}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3767260\charrsid15356049 
